- **Breaking Change**: Document migration path, consider versioned endpoints
- **Large Scope**: Break into small, testable increments per route file","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-11T09:57:22.255410279-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-11T11:07:27.169718509-05:00","closed_at":"2026-01-11T11:07:27.169718509-05:00","close_reason":"All routes updated to use canonical response envelope"}
